channel.title: People cannot join my No-Ip server
channel.description:
For some reason, people cannot join my Fr33sc4p3 based server when I try to run it on No-Ip, although they CAN play when I run it on Hamachi, but I cannot run hamachi right now, so HOW CAN I LET PEOPLE PLAY MY NO-IP SERVER?
Please help, Modest Mouse

item.title: People cannot join my No-Ip server
item.dc:creator: @Modest_Mouse Modest Mouse
item.description:
@Modest_Mouse wrote:

TBH, I used all the guides I could find about “server owning”, although none really helped.

I used to run server on a No-Ip, but in order to do this, I had to d-load Norton 2005, which left me unprotected and ended up with a virus (That’s why I have a new computer…)
